    "name": "Mythos Sandbox API 🏛️",
    "description": "**An interactive sandbox for exploring Ancient Greek mythology.**\n\n**Base URL:** [https://api.qasandbox.org](https://api.qasandbox.org)\n\n---\n\n- **Postman:** [<b>📥 Скачать JSON для импорта в Postman</b>](https://api.qasandbox.ru/swagger.json)\n    \n\n---\n\n### 🛠 Implementation:\n\n- **Auth:** Change methods (**POST**, **PUT**, **PATCH**, **DELETE**) require JWT-token in `Authorization` header.\n    \n- **System Lock:** Entities with **ID 1–31** are protected. Attempted changes return `403 Forbidden`.\n    \n- **Data Mapping:** In API, `desc` field.\n    \n    - In databases it is saved as `description`.\n        \n- **Localization (EN):** `category` uses English as:  \n    `gods`, `heroes`, `creatures`.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
